"В§7 is unique.\n"
"## В§8 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"To prove a statement of the form В§9, first construct a suitable element В§10 "
"and\n"
"then use the В§11 tactic (В§12), usually immediately followed by В§13.\n"
"The proof goal should then have the following form:\n"
"\n"
"В§14\n"
"\n"
"On the left is В§15: you still have to show that В§16 has the required "
"property.\n"
"On the right is the uniqueness statement: every element with this property "
"is equal to В§17.\n"
"\n"
"## В§18 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can prove an assumption of the form В§19 with\n"
"\n"
"В§20\n"
"into its components\n"
"В§21\n"
"."
