#: Game.Doc.Definition
msgid ""
"В§0 means that statements В§1 and В§2 are logically equivalent (вҖңif and only "
"ifвҖқ).\n"
"\n"
"## В§3 as proof target\n"
"\n"
"To show В§4, you can, for example, call В§5\n"
"and then prove В§6 and В§7 separately.\n"
"\n"
"## В§8 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can break down an assumption of the form В§9 using В§10 into its two "
"components\n"
