"| В§5        | В§6 | В§7 and В§8              |\n"
"| В§9   | В§10      | В§11                                    |\n"
"| В§12 | В§13  | В§14 and В§15                     |\n"
"| В§16        | В§17   | a target with В§18, a target with В§19 |\n"
"\n"
"Type the brackets in the first four examples as В§20 or В§21.\n"
"Here, В§22 is the *anonymous constructor*.\n"
"You can think of it as similar to the tuple notation in\n"
"вҖңan abelian group is a tuple В§23 such that ...вҖқ."
